hpfonts/Read_me 12/14/90

hpfonts reorganized 12/13/90 by steve:
Directories:
	etc			Font loading scripts and miscellany from mwc!
	Century		cn*	Century Schoolbook fonts
	Courier		co*	Courier fonts
	Helvetica	hv*	Helvetica fonts
	Humanist	op*	Zapf Humanist fonts
	LinePrinter	lp*	Line Printer fonts
	Other			None of the above fonts
	Prestige	pr*	Prestige fonts
	Times		tr*	Times-Roman fonts

Font names are typically xxdddspn.ccy, where:
	xx	indicates font family name, as above
	ddd	indicates point size in points*10
	s	indicates style, r=Roman b=bold i=italic
	pn	indicates proportional spacing
	cc	indicates character set, typically "us"
	y	indicates orientation, p=portrait l=landscape

Program fwtable (previously called hptable) builds font width tables.
